T02TD2902E:261b-1: badzra dha ra ba lim bi dhi n'a ma /
T02TD2902E:261b-3: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i gtor ma'i cho ga ches bya ba /
T02TD2902E:261b-4: bla ma rje btsun pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2902E:261b-5: las rnams kun gyi sngon 'gro ba //
T02TD2902E:261b-6: bshad phyir bla ma la btud de //
T02TD2902E:261b-7: thams cad tshim par byed pa yi //
T02TD2902E:261b-8: gtor ma'i cho ga de bshad bya //
T02TD2902E:261b-9: de la dang por rdo rje 'dzin /
T02TD2902E:261b-10: sgrub par 'dod pa'i rnal 'byor ba dag gis /
T02TD2902E:261b-11: rin po che las snod rgya che ba bzang la mnyam pa de dag gi nang du /
T02TD2902E:261b-12: 'bras chan la sogs pa chan gyi tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:261b-13: khur ba la sogs pa bza' ba'i tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-2: 'o ma la sogs pa btung ba'i tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-3: bu ram la sogs te myang ba'i tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-4: bil ba la sogs te shing thog gi tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-5: til la sogs te 'bru'i tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-6: autpal la sogs te me tog gi tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-7: aa ga ru la sogs te bdug pa'i tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-8: rin po che la sogs te snang ba'i tshogs dang du ru ka dang dri zhim sbyar ba la sogs te dri'i tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-9: ga bur la sogs te sman gyi tshogs dang /
T02TD2902E:262a-14: ras bzang po la sogs pa ci 'byor ba'i yo byad bshams te /
T02TD2902E:262a-15: mandal sngon po dag gi steng du me tog cha la par bkram la de'i steng du gzhag par bya'o //
T02TD2902E:262a-16: de nas rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid mngon par rtogs pa'i cho ga ltar bskyed la /
T02TD2902E:262a-17: lag pa g-yon pa'i mthil du dri sbyar ba'i chu blugs la /
T02TD2902E:262a-18: aom sarba bi ghn'a na n'a sha ya aa mri ta kunda li ha na ha na h'um zhes lan nyi shu rtsa gcig tu brjod do /
T02TD2902E:262a-19: aom a'a: mi ghn'a nta kri ta h'um phat ces bas gtor ma lan gsum du bya'o //
T02TD2902E:262a-20: de nas yi ge tr'am ser po las bskyed pa'i snod kyi dkyil 'khor gyi nang du /
T02TD2902E:262a-21: rdzas kyi dngos po dpag tu med pa bsams te /
T02TD2902E:262a-22: de'i steng du zla ba'i h'um gis mtshan pa dag gi 'od kyis bsregs shing sbyangs pa'i bdud rtsi'i dngos por gyur par bsam mo //
T02TD2902E:262a-23: de nas thugs ka'i sa bon gyi 'od kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi smin mtshan gyi mdzos spu nas /
T02TD2902E:262a-24: bdud rtsi 'o ma'i rgyun lta bu 'bab pas snod gang bar bsams la /
T02TD2902E:262a-25: aom badzra p'a ni ratna dha r'a ya /
T02TD2902E:262a-26: aom a'a: zhes lan bdun brjod pas byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD2902E:262a-27: de nas snying ga'i sa bon gyi 'od kyis bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'dzin pa spyan drangs la bardza dzi hva zhes lce byin gyis brlabs la sngags 'di lan bdun brjod la dbul bar bya'o //
T02TD2902E:262a-28: aom badzra p'a ni dha r'a ya /
T02TD2902E:262a-29: k'a ya b'a ka tsi tta dh'u pa /
T02TD2902E:262a-33: aa rgha ta ba lim ma da m'am sa ai dam gri kh'a hi kh'a hi bhu nydza ho /
T02TD2902E:262a-35: aa ti kra ma ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD2902E:262a-36: de nas thugs ka'i sa bon gyi 'od kyis khams gsum gyi 'byung po'i tshogs ma lus pa bkug ste /
T02TD2902E:262a-37: aom badzra h'um ga ra ka ta ka ta phat /
T02TD2902E:262a-39: de thams cad rdo rje 'dzin gyi ngo bor gyur par bsams te /
T02TD2902E:262b-0: yi ge gsum bkod la lce @262b byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD2902E:262b-1: de nas aom aa k'a ro mu khi sarba dha rm'a n'am a'a dya nutpann tv'ata /
T02TD2902E:262b-4: de nas 'byung po'i tshogs de dag mnyes par gyur nas /
T02TD2902E:262b-5: rgyal bar gyur cig ces brjod par bsam mo //
T02TD2902E:262b-6: de nas lag tu me tog thogs te /
T02TD2902E:262b-7: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab la /
T02TD2902E:262b-9: h'um lhag pa dang ni chad pas kyang //
T02TD2902E:262b-10: bdag gis brjed ngas gang bgyis pa //
T02TD2902E:262b-11: mgon po khyod kyis bzod mdzad nas //
T02TD2902E:262b-12: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
T02TD2902E:262b-14: aom khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
T02TD2902E:262b-15: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
T02TD2902E:262b-16: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
T02TD2902E:262b-17: slar yang 'byor par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD2902E:262b-18: aom a'a:h'um mu: zhes pas gshegs su gsol //
T02TD2902E:262b-19: de nas phyag rgya bkrol te /
T02TD2902E:262b-20: gtor ma gtsang ma'i sa phyogs su bskyal la /
T02TD2902E:262b-22: rdo rje 'dzin pa mchod pa'i phyir//
T02TD2902E:262b-23: mchod sbyin 'di brtsams bsod nams kyis //
T02TD2902E:262b-24: 'gro ba thams cad rgyas gyur te //
T02TD2902E:262b-25: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob shog / rdo rje'i 'dzin pa'i gtor ma'i cho ga rdzogs so /
T02TD2902E:262b-27: // / slob dpon ba su dha badzras mdzad pa'o//
